---
titleFull: "ISC2 Tampa Bay – Connecting Tampa Bay's Information Security Professionals"
description: "ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter connects information security professionals in the Tampa Bay area through networking, education, and community events."
layout: base.njk
---

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container hero-content">
      <div class="hero-badge">Tampa Bay's #1 InfoSec Community</div>
      <h1>Connecting Tampa Bay's <span>Information Security</span> Professionals</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Join 300+ cybersecurity professionals for quarterly meetings, hands-on training, and the annual <a href="https://bsidestampa.net" style="color:var(--green-light);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;">BSides Tampa</a> conference.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/membership/" class="btn">Become a Member</a>
        <a href="/events/" class="btn-outline btn-outline--light">View Events →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bar -->
  <section class="stats-bar">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">300+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Active Members</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Years Active</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">6+</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Events Per Year</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-number">501(c)(3)</span>
        <span class="stat-label">Nonprofit</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Split Section -->
  <section class="split-section" id="main-content">
    <div class="container split-grid">
      <div class="split-text">
        <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2>Tampa Bay's Home for InfoSec Professionals</h2>
        <p>The ISC2 Tampa Bay Chapter brings together information security professionals across the West-Central Florida area. Whether you hold a CISSP, SSCP, or are just getting started in cybersecurity, our chapter offers quarterly meetings, hands-on training, and a community that helps you grow.</p>
        <p>We're also the official host of the annual <a href="https://bsidestampa.net"><strong>BSides Tampa</strong></a> conference.</p>
        <a href="/about/" class="text-link">Learn more about us →</a>
      </div>
      <div class="split-media">
        <div class="photo-collage">
          <img src="/images/meeting2.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter meeting" class="animate-on-scroll">
          <img src="/images/meeting1.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter event" class="animate-on-scroll">
          <img src="/images/meeting3.jpeg" alt="ISC2 Tampa Bay chapter networking" class="animate-on-scroll">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="features-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <span class="section-label">What to Expect</span>
        <h2>A Typical Chapter Meeting</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature-card animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18.06 22.99h1.66c.84 0 1.53-.64 1.63-1.46L23 5.05h-5V1h-1.97v4.05h-4.97l.3 2.34c1.71.47 3.31 1.32 4.27 2.26 1.44 1.42 2.43 2.89 2.43 5.29v8.05zM1 21.99V21h15.03v.99c0 .55-.45 1-1.01 1H2.01c-.56 0-1.01-.45-1.01-1zm15.03-7c0-4.5-6.97-5-9.03-5h-1v7h1c2.06 0 9.03-.5 9.03-5zM1.02 17h15v2h-15z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Breakfast & Check-in</h3>
          <p>Arrive to complimentary breakfast and snacks while you connect with fellow security professionals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v18l4-4h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H6l-2 2V4h16v12z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Presentations & Talks</h3>
          <p>Two speaking sessions featuring industry experts on current cybersecurity topics, with officer updates in between.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5C6.34 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Networking & Lunch</h3>
          <p>Midday break with a provided lunch — the best part of every meeting for building lasting professional connections.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Upcoming Events -->
  <section class="upcoming-preview">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label" style="text-align:center;display:block;">Coming Up</span>
      <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
      {% set eventCount = 0 %}
      {% for event in events %}
        {% if event.date | isFuture and eventCount < 2 %}
          {% set eventCount = eventCount + 1 %}
          <div class="upcoming-card animate-on-scroll">
            <div class="upcoming-date">
              <span class="upcoming-month">{{ event.date | dateMonth }}</span>
              <span class="upcoming-day">{{ event.date | dateDay }}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="upcoming-info">
              <h3>{{ event.title }}</h3>
              <p>{{ event | formatEventTime }} · {{ event.location }}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
      <a href="/events/" class="text-link" style="display:inline-flex;margin-top:20px;">View All Events →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Banner -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to connect with Tampa Bay's security community?</h2>
      <p class="cta-subtitle">Join our chapter and get access to quarterly meetings, training events, and a network of cybersecurity professionals.</p>
      <div class="cta-banner-actions">
        <a href="/membership/" class="btn">Become a Member</a>
        <a href="/volunteer/" class="btn-outline btn-outline--light">Volunteer</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="mission">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Our Mission</span>
      <h2>Mission <span>Driven</span></h2>
      <p>The Tampa Bay Chapter of ISC2 advances the knowledge of information security professionals, students, and practitioners through education, training, and community engagement.</p>
      <div class="callout">
        <p style="margin:0;"><a href="https://bsidestampa.net"><strong>BSides Tampa</strong></a> — We're the official host of Tampa Bay's annual information technology security conference, bringing together researchers, practitioners, and students.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="focus-areas">
        <span class="focus-pill">Network Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Cloud Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Penetration Testing</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Digital Forensics</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Cryptography</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Data Privacy</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Software Security</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">CTF Competitions</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Malware Analysis</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">Social Engineering</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">CISSP Training</span>
        <span class="focus-pill">SSCP Training</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mission-note">The Tampa Bay chapter of ISC2 is a registered 501(c)(3) educational non-profit. All donations are tax deductible under section 501(c)(3) of the Internal Revenue Code.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
